<P>BRother, if you meete with your <HI>Iethro's</HI> counsel
returned from beyond the seas, and as much
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> your expectation preserued aliue, as his
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> in law was against <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"></HI> Iniunction, mer|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">
