<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> you haue cause. <HI>Ioab</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> wider on the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word">
hand in destroying <HI>Dauids Absolon,</HI> contrary
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> be serious charge, yet <HI>Ioab</HI> was pardoned, and
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> no brother. I haue noted you hitherto inexora|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="3 letters">
for your owne publishing of any thing of your
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word">&punc; whether out of iudgement, modesty, curio|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">&punc;
or melancholy, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> iudge not: but when others
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 span"> them with fruit and acceptance&punc;
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word"> the light, I haue seene you rest content with
